{"root":{"data":{"id":"1694ae1dd2e6","created":1562511307,"text":"React 生命周期","note":"- https://zh-hans.reactjs.org/docs/react-component.html\n\n- http://projects.wojtekmaj.pl/react-lifecycle-methods-diagram/"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bvgxqw3a80w0","created":1562899817164,"text":"第一次","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bvgxqeydh9c0","created":1562899779862,"text":"constructor","note":"- 如果不初始化 state 或不进行方法绑定，则不需要为 React 组件实现构造函数。\n\n通常，在 React 中，构造函数仅用于以下两种情况：\n\n- 通过给 this.state 赋值对象来初始化内部 state。\n- 为事件处理函数绑定实例"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxqh1asco0","created":1562899784392,"text":"getDerivedStateFromProps","note":"- 会在调用 render 方法之前调用，并且在初始挂载及后续更新时都会被调用。它应返回一个对象来更新 state，如果返回 null 则不更新任何内容。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxqppic3c0","created":1562899803270,"text":"render"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxrhmo1400","created":1562899864048,"text":"componentDidMount","note":"- 会在组件挂载后（插入 DOM 树中）立即调用。依赖于 DOM 节点的初始化应该放在这里。如需通过网络请求获取数据，此处是实例化请求的好地方。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxr2qznkg0","created":1562899831658,"text":"再次渲染","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bvgxrqma7io0","created":1562899883616,"text":"getDerivedStateFromProps","note":"- 在最近一次渲染输出（提交到 DOM 节点）之前调用。它使得组件能在发生更改之前从 DOM 中捕获一些信息（例如，滚动位置）。此生命周期的任何返回值将作为参数传递给 componentDidUpdate()。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxugpxog00","created":1562900097162,"text":"shouldComponetUpdate"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxrxwddd40","created":1562899899464,"text":"render"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxs01l7wg0","created":1562899904133,"text":"getSnapshotBeforeUpdate","note":"- 在最近一次渲染输出（提交到 DOM 节点）之前调用。它使得组件能在发生更改之前从 DOM 中捕获一些信息（例如，滚动位置）。此生命周期的任何返回值将作为参数传递给 componentDidUpdate()。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxs5ivj7s0","created":1562899916062,"text":"componentDidUpdate","note":"- 当组件更新后，可以在此处对 DOM 进行操作。如果你对更新前后的 props 进行了比较，也可以选择在此处进行网络请求。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxuzd13c80","created":1562900137740,"text":"卸载"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bvgxv3nl7ew0","created":1562900147086,"text":"componentWillUnmount"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxvjawxls0","created":1562900181148,"text":"错误处理"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bvgxvt1vrlk0","created":1562900202370,"text":"getDerivedStatrFromError"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bvgxw692aso0","created":1562900231102,"text":"componentDidCatch"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}